                Accidentes de Trabajo (ART)
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="group bg-white p-10 rounded-[30px] shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(217,119,83,0.15)] transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 relative overflow-hidden">
