                    Te explicamos tu situación legal sin tecnicismos complejos. Queremos que entiendas tus opciones reales.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-5 group">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-bg-soft)] flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--color-primary)] group-hover:bg-[var(--color-accent)] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                </div>
