                <p class="font-serif text-xl italic leading-relaxed mb-8 opacity-90">
                  "Nuestro objetivo no es solo ganar un caso, sino devolverle la tranquilidad al cliente. La confianza se construye con resultados, pero se mantiene con honestidad."
                </p>
                
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white text-lg">MD</div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-bold text-white">Maria Fernanda Diodati</p>
                    <p class="text-[var(--color-accent)] text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Abogada Titular</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
             </div>

             <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-full h-full border-2 border-[var(--color-accent)] rounded-tr-[80px] rounded-bl-[80px] z-0 opacity-30"></div>

          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-[var(--color-primary)] text-white relative overflow-hidden">
      
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.05]" 
           style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 10px, #D97753 10px, #D97753 11px);">
      </div>
      
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-[var(--color-primary-light)]/20 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[var(--color-accent)] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-2 block">Tu tranquilidad, paso a paso</span>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">El camino hacia la solución</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 relative">
          
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-0 w-full h-[2px] bg-white/10 -z-10"></div>

          <div class="group relative">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-[var(--color-primary)] border-4 border-[var(--color-accent)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-6 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(217,119,83,0.3)] group-hover:bg-[var(--color-accent)] group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500">
              1
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-center">Consulta Inicial</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm text-center leading-relaxed px-4">
              Analizamos tu caso en profundidad. Te escuchamos y evaluamos la documentación para darte un diagnóstico honesto y claro.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="group relative">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-[var(--color-primary)] border-4 border-[var(--color-accent)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-6 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(217,119,83,0.3)] group-hover:bg-[var(--color-accent)] group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500 delay-150">
              2
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-center">Estrategia</h3>
